Machine Overview
Machine Name: Overpass
Â Target IP: 10.10.xxx.xxx
Â Operating System: Linux (Ubuntu-based)
This assessment focused on client-side authentication bypass, credential recovery through exposed cryptographic material, and privilege escalation via a misconfigured cron job.

